'''2MASS J0523−1403'''是一顆位於南天[[星座|星座]][[天兔座|天兔座]]，距離地球大約40[[光年|光年]]，質量非常低的[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://astronomy.stackexchange.com/questions/40198/how-do-we-know-that-2mass-j0523-1403-is-a-red-dwarf|title=Star - How do we know that 2MASS J0523-1403 is a red dwarf?|access-date=2022-04-26|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514103327/https://astronomy.stackexchange.com/questions/40198/how-do-we-know-that-2mass-j0523-1403-is-a-red-dwarf}}</ref>。它的視星等非常黯淡，只有21.05等，表面有效溫度僅2,074[[熱力學溫標|K]]，要對[[紅外線|紅外線]]敏感的大型望遠鏡才看得見它。這顆恆星是在[[2微米全天巡天|2微米全天巡天]] （2MASS）時首度觀測到<ref name=Cruz_2003>{{cite journal|last=Cruz|first=Kelle L.|last2 = Reid | first2 = I. Neill|last3 = Liebert | first3 = James | last4 = Kirkpatrick | first4 = J. Davy | last5 = Lowrance | first5 = Patrick J. | title = Meeting the Cool Neighbors. V. A 2MASS-Selected Sample of Ultracool Dwarfs | journal = [[The_Astronomical_Journal|The Astronomical Journal]] | date = 2003 | volume = 126 | issue = 5 | pages = 2421–2448 | doi = 10.1086/378607 | arxiv = astro-ph/0307429 | bibcode = 2003AJ....126.2421C }}</ref>。

== 特徵 ==

2MASS J0523−1403的[[亮度|亮度]]約為{{Solar luminosity|link=y|0.000126}}，半徑為{{Solar radius|link=y|0.086}}，和[[有效溫度|有效溫度]]2,074 [[熱力學溫標|K]]。這些數值都是目前所知[[主序星|主序星]]的最低值<ref name=Dieterich_2013>{{cite journal | last = Dieterich | first = Sergio B. | last2 = Henry | first2 = Todd J. | last3 = Jao | first3 = Wei-Chun | last4 = Winters | first4 = Jennifer G. | last5 = Hosey | first5 = Altonio D. | last6 = Riedel | first6 = Adric R. | last7 = Subasavage | first7 = John P. | title = The Solar Neighborhood XXXII. The Hydrogen Burning Limit | journal = [[The_Astronomical_Journal|The Astronomical Journal]] | volume = 147 | issue = 5 | at = article id 94 | date = May 2014 | doi = 10.1088/0004-6256/147/5/94 | bibcode = 2014AJ....147...94D | arxiv = 1312.1736 }}</ref>。它的[[恆星光譜|光譜類型]]為L2.5，V-K[[色指數|色指數]]為9.42  <ref name=Dieterich_2013 />。計算得到的質量估計為{{jupiter mass|{{val|67.54|12.79}}}}（{{solar mass|{{val|0.0644|0.0122}}}}）<ref name=filippazzo/>。[[哈伯太空望遠鏡|哈伯太空望遠鏡]]觀測在0.15[[角秒|角秒]]的範圍之外沒有伴星存在<ref name=Reid_2006>{{cite journal|last=Reid|first=I. Neill|last2=Lewitus | first2 = E.| last3 = Allen | first3 = P. R.| last4 = Cruz | first4 = Kelle L.| last5 = Burgasser | first5 = Adam J. | title = A Search for Binary Systems among the Nearest L Dwarfs|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_astronomical-journal_2006-08_132_2/page/891|journal=[[The_Astronomical_Journal|The Astronomical Journal]] | date = 2006 | volume = 132 | issue = 2 | pages = 891–901 | doi = 10.1086/505626| arxiv = astro-ph/0606331 | bibcode = 2006AJ....132..891R }}</ref>。在2004年通過[[甚大天線陣|甚大天線陣]]（VLA，Very Large Array）檢測到零星的電波輻射<ref name=Antonova_2007>{{cite journal | last = Antonova | first = A. | last2 = Doyle | first2 = J. G. | last3 = Hallinan | first3 = G. | last4 = Golden | first4 = A. | last5 = Koen | first5 = C. | title = Sporadic long-term variability in radio activity from a brown dwarf | journal = [[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]] | date = 2 September 2007 | volume = 472 | issue = 1 | pages = 257–260 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20077231 |  arxiv = 0707.0634 | bibcode = 2007A&A...472..257A }}</ref>。 [[H-α|H-α]]的輻射也被檢測到，而這是[[色球|色球]]活動的一個跡象<ref name=Reiners_2008 />。

== 氫融合極限 ==
[[近星研究會|近星研究會]]（RECONS）的成員最近確認2MASS J0523-1403可能是最小恆星的代表<ref name=Garmany_2013>{{cite press release | last=Garmany | first=Katy | title=NOAO/SOAR: Where do stars end and brown dwarfs begin? | url=http://www.noao.edu/news/2013/pr1311.php | publisher=National Optical Astronomy Observatory | date=9 December 2013 | accessdate=14 December 2013 | archive-date=2020-01-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112075908/https://www.noao.edu/news/2013/pr1311.php | dead-url=no }}</ref>。它的半徑-亮度和半徑-溫度都是[[極值|本地]]最小的<ref name=Dieterich_2013 />。由於主序星和[[棕矮星|棕矮星]]的半徑-質量關係不同，本地最小值發生在[[恆星核合成|氫燃燒]]的極限。與棕矮星不同的是，它們的核心由[[簡併態物質|簡併壓力]]支撐，所以棕矮星的半徑隨著質量增加而減小。即當棕矮星的質量增加，也增加了簡併的分數，導致半徑隨著質量的增加而縮小<ref name=Garmany_2013/>。 理論估計恆星的最低質量在0.07至0.077{{Solar mass}}之間，與2MASS J0523-1403的質量與此相符<ref name="Dieterich_2013" />。

